.BI "SDL_Surface* SDL_LoadBMP_IO(SDL_IOStream *src, SDL_bool closeio);
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
The new surface should be freed with

.BR SDL_DestroySurface
()\[char46] Not doing so will result in a
memory leak\[char46]

